::DarkMouse::

She looked back at Quickstrike.
"Do you have any instructions for me commander?"
She felt about an inch tall standing next to him.  She was starting to like 
him.  And yet she knew that she never had a chance.  She thought of 
Scorponok.  She liked him too.  But same thing, there were other female bots 
around that they must have liked more than her.
She smiled at Quickstrike. It was a small and almost shy smile. She wanted 
her commanders happy with her and her work.
"If it pleases you commander, please take a look at the tunnel.  I hope you 
like it.  I did everything I could think of to make it invisible from the 
outside. An it is sturdy.  We can take many blasts and it won't collapse."
She got up and walked to the escape tunnel.
